    "image_with_text_9WEiBt": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_Qjbd39": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Q: What’s your favourite childhood snack?</h3><p>Pearl: I ate a lot of sugary cereals. My favourite was Reese Puffs and Chef Boyardee. </p><p>Dickson: Haw flakes. If you don’t know what those are, look them up. And then, Maltesers. Not Whoppers, Maltesers, don’t get it twisted.</p><h3>Q: How would you describe your style?</h3><p>Pearl: Kind of all over the place. But usually street, a little bit of vintage, and a little bit funky.</p><p>Dickson: And then my style has a bit of streetwear, skate, techwear, whatever the vibe is or the trend.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
